程序包 com.ae2dms

类 Main

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
com.ae2dms.Main
public class Main
extends javafx.application.Application
The Sokoban program implements a game that players need to push the boxes to the target using the fewest steps and time. Have fun and enjoy!

The entry point of the game. This class launch a application window.

    • main

      public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)

      参数:

    • start

      public void start​(javafx.stage.Stage primaryStage) throws java.lang.Exception
      This method loads the window, includes the menu and primary stage.

      File includes Save Game, Load Game, Exit.

      Level includes Undo, Toggle Music, Toggle Debug, Reset Level.

      About includes About This Game.

      指定者:
      start 在类中 javafx.application.Application
      参数:
      primaryStage - Stage type. As the primary stage to set the window.
      抛出:
      java.lang.Exception - Unused. --On input error.--
